{
  "_comment": "Ablation: disable the regime raw-weight filter by setting raw_uncertain and teacher_only raw_weight = 1.0 (production uses 0.0 for both). All other hyperparameters mirror the production anchor_off config. Quantifies the negative effect of right-censored late-time frames when admitted as raw supervision.",
